719
00:51:09,441 --> 00:51:11,193
- Mãe?
- Dou-te tudo o que quiseres.

720
00:51:13,028 --> 00:51:16,448
Sarah, por favor não testemunhes.

721
00:51:22,788 --> 00:51:23,956
<i>Vão!</i>

722
00:51:27,251 --> 00:51:28,168
<i>Vão!</i>

723
00:51:48,147 --> 00:51:49,440
<i>Abrir fogo!</i>

724
00:51:49,898 --> 00:51:51,066
<i>Cubram!</i>

725
00:52:16,759 --> 00:52:18,344
<i>Temos de confiar uns nos outros.</i>

726
00:52:22,765 --> 00:52:24,224
<i>Temos de pedir ajuda.</i>

727
00:52:27,895 --> 00:52:30,731
- Obrigado por vires.
